high_descs: Go right and stand in front of the sink and then turn left to face the counter.
Pick the lettuce up from the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and then open the fridge and take the lettuce out and shut the door.
Turn around and approach the stove and then go left to and face the trash can.
Put the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in the trash can.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the stove
pick up lettuce from the counter
move to the fridge behind you
chill the lettuce for a moment in the fridge
Move to the bin to the left of the stove
put the lettuce in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the bin.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward, hanging a left when you reach the fridge, then walk up to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the lettuce that is sitting on the counter.
Turn around and head over to the fridge.
Cool off the lettuce in the fridge before pulling it back out.
Turn around and walk over to the green bin sitting to the left of the stove.
Place the lettuce in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Place cooled off lettuce into a bin.
